      </tr> 
      <tr> 
       <td>Day Portal Director HTTP Client Service</td> 
       <td>Configure how the portlet connects via HTTP to underlying AEM WCM instances. You can, for example, specify a proxy server.</td> 
      </tr> 
      <tr> 
       <td>Day Portal Director Locale Handler</td> 
       <td>Configure which locales the portlet supports. Requests to AEM WCM instances are based on the user locale; for example, user language <em>German </em>would request <span class="code">/content/geometrixx/de/</span>....</td> 
      </tr> 
      <tr> 
